      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSHINE RHONDA (7) started big odds in tougher last time when finishing 7th over 515m at this track. Won an easier race the start before that at this track. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can atone. RIE BALE (2) did a good job to finish second last time out over 400m at this track (23.10) in a Mix 2/3, the second top-three finish on the trot. Can find the frame this time. INDIGO PEARL (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 515m behind Larrikin Pioneer (30.23) in a Grade 5. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. WRECK IT REX (8) comes here off a freshen-up and must be included.",
